sourcesContent: import React, { Fragment } from 'react' import Title from './Home/Title' import Home from './Home' import FormPost from './FormPost' import Post from './Post' import EditFormPost from './EditFormPost' import EditPost from './EditForm' import { BrowserRouter as Router, Switch, Route, NavLink } from "react-router-dom"; const Body = () => { return ( <Router> <div className="btn-group my-3"> <NavLink to="/" exact className="btn btn-light" activeClassName="active">Home</NavLink> <NavLink to="/edit-post" exact className="btn btn-light" activeClassName="active">Editar Post</NavLink> </div> <Switch> <Route path="/save-post" component={FormPost} /> <Route path="/edit-post" component={EditPost} /> <Route path="/post/id=:id" component={Post} /> <Route path="/edit-post/id=:id" component={EditFormPost} /> <Route path="/" component={Home} /> </Switch> </Router> </Fragment> ) } export default Body
